				</choice>
				<choice hidden="true">
					<text>Follow your Shell's advice and leave.</text>
					<event>
						<text>The Slaver ship continues to advertise their "products", so you simply mute all hails coming from their ship.</text>
						<choice>
							<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
							<event load="STORAGE_CHECK"/>
						</choice>
						<choice>
							<text>Do nothing.</text>
							<event/>
						</choice>
					</event>
				</choice>
			</event>
		</choice>
		<choice>
			<text>This is shady, let's leave.</text>
			<event>
				<text>The Slaver ship continues to advertise their "products", so you simply mute all hails coming from their ship.</text>
				<choice>
					<text>Do something onboard the ship.</text>
