	<mod:findName type="event" name="SLAVER_BETRAYAL">
		<mod-append:choice req="rep_comb_slaver" lvl="2">
			<text>(Slaver rep 2+) Request info on the slave.</text>
			<event>
				<text>"What? Who are you to make such demands? Nobody gets any extras on such a great deal! Now, for the last time, are you gonna take this outstanding deal or be an idiot?" Seems like these slavers aren't a part of Tiiikaka anymore, so your reputation won't get you any special treatment from them.</text>
