  <event name="ZOLTAN_LECTURE_MARKET" unique="true">
	<text>A Zoltan peace brigade is lecturing some pirates on the importance of good morals. You stop in to watch in amusement when one of the pirates gets impatient and attacks. You're too close to get away, so you have to decide which side you're going to have to take.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Side with the Zoltans.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You ready yourself for combat.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_PIRATE_LECTURE_MARKET" hostile="true"/> 
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="REPUTATION_DECREASE_PIRATES_COMBAT"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Side with the pirates.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You ready yourself for combat.</text>
			<ship load="SHIP_ZOLTAN_LECTURE_MARKET" hostile="true"/> 
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="MORALITY_UPDATE_ZOLTAN_FIGHT"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
  </event>
	
  <event name="ZOLTAN_LECTURE_MARKET_WIN_PIRATE" unique="true">
	<text>You successfully dispatch the Zoltan ship. You notice the Zoltan forces are retreating, and it appears the pirates won. You scrap the Zoltan ship quickly.</text>
	<autoReward level="LOW">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Contact your pirate "brethren".</text>
		<event>
			<text>"Say, that was some good fightin' kid. Thanks for the help. I'm sure I have something to repay you." You're surprised at the pirates' gratitude and are suspicious of a trick, but the cargo crate they deliver you is surprisingly harmless and contains a shiny new military class weapon.</text>
			<autoReward level="MED">weapon</autoReward>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="REPUTATION_UPDATE_PIRATES_FREE"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
  </event>
	
  <event name="ZOLTAN_LECTURE_MARKET_WIN_ZOLTAN" unique="true">
	<text>You successfully dispatch the pirate ship. You notice the pirates are retreating, and it appears the Zoltan won. You scrap your victim quickly.</text>
	<autoReward level="MED">standard</autoReward>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Contact the Zoltan brigade.</text>
		<event>
			<text>"We were not expecting Federation reinforcements. Your help is much appreciated. As is Zoltan custom, we are now in your debt and shall pay it off dutifully."</text>
			<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Continue...</text>
				<event load="MORALITY_REMOVE_ZOLTAN"/>
			</choice>
		</event>
	</choice>
  </event>


