	<event name="PIP_MARKET_SLAVE_GLADIATORS_BET_3_WIN_CHEAT_ESCAPE">
		<text>Somehow, by sheer, stupid luck you manage to slip away undetected. Whether the pirates know about the illegal stimulants or whether they just can't find who applied them will remain a mystery to you, but you don't want to stick around to find out. You're just glad that the pirates running the show are a bunch of idiots.</text>
	</event>
	<event name="PIP_MARKET_SLAVE_GLADIATORS_BET_3_WIN_CHEAT_CAUGHT">
		<text>As you're preparing to leave, an enforcer moves forward to block your path. Seems like you weren't as unnoticed as you thought, because the enforcer is now demanding that you pay them back a majority of the winnings that you won illegally.</text>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Refuse and run!</text>
			<event>
				<text>You pretend to consider returning the winnings, but then swiftly draw your own blaster to shoot the enforcer. The wounded enforcer yells for his companions to chase after you before passing out. While a squad of fighter slaves are beamed aboard from the station and a slaver ship flies out to engage, sensors also indicate that an ASB has locked on to your ship!</text>
				<boarders min="2" max="3" class="LIST_SLAVES_FIGHTER_GLADIATOR_GOOD"/>
				<environment target="player" type="PDS"/>
				<variable name="loc_gladiators_cheat" op="set" val="2"/>
				<ship load="PIP_GLADIATOR_ENFORCER_2" hostile="true"/>
				<choice hidden="true">
					<text>Continue...</text>
