	<event name="PIP_MARKET_SLAVE_GLADIATORS_BET_4_WIN">
		<text>You aren't sure what you expected by betting on a Separatist, but things turn out far better than you expected. The Separatist managed to get an easy bracket for the most part, and when they reach the last Soldier which you could've bet on, the Separatist manages to outsmart the tired Soldier with a few good dodges and narrowly wins the interaction. Amidst the enormous hype surrounding the entire station, you claim your winnings!</text>
