			<item type="scrap" min="200" max="200"/>
		</item_modify>
	</event>
	<event name="PIP_MARKET_SLAVE_GLADIATORS_BET_4_LOSE">
		<text>As expected, the Separatist is quickly taken out by a mere Phantom in the first round. Their tournament run ended so quickly that upon returning to your ship, you realise you still have time to do something before you have to get going. You make a mental note to take on more favourable gambles in the future.</text>
