			<event/>
		</choice>
	</event>

	<event name="PIP_MARKET_SLAVE_GLADIATORS_BET_4_LOSE_CHEAT">
		<text>Unfortunately, the stimulants weren't enough for the Separatist to overcome a Rockman. Though they made it farther than most would expect, it still falls short of a tournament win, leaving you with no winnings. You hasten to leave before the pirates can find out about your illegal stimulants.</text>
