				<text>You successfully manage to slip away undetected. You power up the ship and prepare to jump.</text>
			</event>
			<event>
				<text>Just as you thought you could escape without being caught, you hear one of the enforcers yelling at you to report back to them for suspicious behaviour around the Separatist. You decide to make a break for it and run to your ship. Luckily, most of the enforcers seem to be dealing with a more serious case of cheating, but a few of them chase you all the way back to your ship.</text>
