			</event>
		</choice>
	</event>
	
	<event name="PIP_MARKET_SLAVE_GLADIATORS_BET_4_WIN_CHEAT">
		<text>The stimulants manage to help the Separatist even the playing field on most fights. With a bit of luck and calculated attacks, the Separatist emerges victorious on most fights and just barely manages to take down the Rock Cultist. You move forward to claim your winnings.</text>
