			<item type="scrap" min="200" max="200"/>
		</item_modify>
		<choice req="LIST_CHECK_ANY_CREW" lvl="1" blue="false" hidden="true">
			<text>Attempt to leave.</text>
			<event>
				<text>As you're preparing to leave with your crew, one of the enforcers moves forward to block your path. "Look, pal. We understand that you're just trying to squeeze as much scrap as you can out of every opportunity you find. Trouble is, this tournament was not supposed to be one of those opportunities. My men highly suspect that you provided illegal stimulants to the slave you bet on, and it doesn't look good when a slave that nobody expects to win gets their first win on a day when some Federation captain decides to bet on them. I understand that you're decently well-known around these parts, and it would be a shame for it to end this way. So, I'll allow you to walk away with a very small portion of the winnings if you'll forfeit the remainder to us." Before you can consider making your reply, you notice the other enforcers slowly reaching for their guns, and your crew start to reach for their blasters as well. Every eye seems to be on you and your crew. This could be very nasty if you reject the enforcer's offer.</text>
